{"tid":608588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[人手取代科技]楊偉雄認申科技券輪候時間長　會安排加人手","createTime":"2018-03-28T09:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T14:37:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bba8c0e6fa40a047da110594adc9a199b5c7eaaf","tid":608588,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"創新科技署於前年底推出科技券計劃，資助本地中小企業使用科技服務或方案提高生產力或升級轉型，惟有部分公司申請輪候時間極長，最後更不獲審批，其原因乃文件不足，質疑創科局與申請者溝通不足。立法會議員鍾國斌對此提出質詢，追問科技券自推出以來的申請狀況。<br />\n<br />\n創科局局長楊偉雄指，科技券自推出以來，截至今年2月底共有889宗申請，包括批發及零售業、進出口業、專業服務等，當中403宗已獲處理，有377宗獲批，佔94%。申請日數方面，楊偉雄指最快和最慢的個案分別是14個和175個工作天，平均則是約80個工作天，承認對進度並不滿意，會就工作需要<span style=\"color: red;\">安排增加人手</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/bkn-20180328122702052-0328_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fbkn-20180328122702052-0328_00822_001.html&d=pCGlbbMDkhoO14P0X15fkmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=636acbc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/bkn-20180328122702052-0328_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9258ca21e45439babe65b8c2a12272baa269d58e","tid":608588,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45673eb7da87dc7390382630879b5f036f850acb","tid":608588,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"Manual Mode?"},{"pid":"1c88c6fa5f73916de57f8a5e10a34baa8f1dde6d","tid":608588,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b0b20b133c08aad017d05357bbe10d8f1